beer.beer_description: A velvety medium-bodied brew at 8.5% ABV, Back Home Gingerbread Stout is brewed with fresh ginger and a balanced blend of secret spices. Notes of cinnamon, nutmeg, candied orange peel and vanilla dance with rich chocolate malt for a festive holiday treat. Hops: Bravo and Northern Brewer. Malts: 2-Row, Crystal 160, Pale Chocolate, Carafa, Roast Barley. IBU: 45.
